articles.title: About Stephanie's blog
articles.description: "Even though you're growing up, you should never stop having fun." -Nina Dobrev.
articles.contents: Hi peeps! I’m a Malaysian currently studying in Monash Clayton, Melbourne. I’m enrolled in Master of Business Analytics. I would say it is really challenging for me but I enjoyed each bits and pieces of it. I would like to share more interesting stuffs on this blog in the future, so stay tuned!
